  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b9c\u0ba9 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0b9e\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b86\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bae\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 - \u0b9f\u0bbf.\u0bb5\u0bbf.\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0b95",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Podujana Peramuna's youth team support for Ranil Wickramasinghe - TV Chanaka",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The youth wing of Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna has decided to vote for the candidate nominated by Podujana Peramuna during the new presidential election.",
        "Member of Parliament T.V. Sanaka said that this decision was taken during the Central Executive Committee meeting of the Youth League of Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna.",
        "He also mentioned that all the members of the youth team have agreed to the decision of Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna to support Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "Podujana Peramuna General Secretary Sagara Kariyawasam has announced that he will support the nomination of President Ranil Wickremesinghe for the post of President.",
        "Meanwhile, while Dines Gunawardena, the Speaker of the House, Ranil Wickramasinghe was nominated for the post of President, Member of Parliament Manusha Nanayakkara confirmed it. However, it is noteworthy that the other side of the Podujana Peramuna has declared its support for the Dallas beauty."
      ],
